column1: #Text=What do you most value in your friends ?
#Text=I like people who are driven , passionate , ambitious , but very witty and knowledgeable , but good people .
#Text=Do you keep a large circle of friends or do you tend to keep it close ?
#Text=How many friends do you have that if you were to self-destruct , they would be there for you ?
#Text=Close friends like I asked you about ?
#Text=I keep it pretty close or I find it too overwhelming because I am always working on projects and I need to concentrate .
#Text=If I was to self destruct I would say four people that would be there .
#Text=Yeah , I mean I did n't count in my mom and my dad ...
#Text=If you self-destructed how many people could you count on to stay by you ?
#Text=Is that including all the girl ? [ Laughs ]
#Text=Did you include Sune in your count ?
#Text=Within the band , our drummer in Denmark is my really good friend , because we have been living such a crazy life together for so long that we just became so close .
#Text=And over here I might have maybe five , six people , maybe .
#Text=As your fame has increased , have you found it more difficult to trust people ?
#Text=I have n't experienced anything like that .
#Text=I have found it easier to meet people .
#Text=But I have n't found too many phonies , and I have n't had a problem with that .
#Text=I do n't go out much , and when I go out I just usually go out with my friends and I 'll occasionally go out to see a show .
#Text=So , I really do n't meet that many people .
#Text=And the people I meet on the road are fans and stuff , and I always try to be polite and accommodate them as best I can .
#Text=Do you guys see an end to the band , a day when you can see yourselves feeling done with it ?
#Text=I guess sometimes we think about if we want to start a family or something like that .
#Text=Or maybe there will be other priorities at a certain point ...
#Text=we joke about it a lot , actually ...
